msgstr "Kōwhiringa"

msgctxt "#31210"
msgid "Select another image as default background"
msgstr "Tīpakohia tētahi atu atahanga hei papamuri taunoa"

msgctxt "#31211"
msgid "Changes the default Aeon Tajo background to another chosen by the user."
msgstr "Ka huri i te papamuri Aeon Tajo taunoa ki tetahi atu i kowhiria e te kaiwhakamahi."

msgctxt "#31212"
msgid "Current background path: "
msgstr "Ara papamuri onāianei:"

msgctxt "#31213"
msgid "Reset skin default background"
msgstr "Tautuhi ano i te papamuri taunoa kiri"

msgctxt "#31214"
msgid "Resets the default background provided with Aeon Tajo."
msgstr "Ka tautuhi ano i te papamuri taunoa me Aeon Tajo."

msgctxt "#31215"
msgid "Show the coloured version of the icons rather than the monochrome version."
msgstr "Whakaatuhia te putanga tae o nga ata kaua ki te putanga monochrome."

msgctxt "#31216"
msgid "Displays background and fanart images with a subtle motion effect across the screen."
msgstr "Ka whakaatu i nga whakaahua papamuri me nga whakaahua fanart me te awenga nekehanga ngawari puta noa i te mata."

msgctxt "#31217"
msgid "Displays a list in the video views featuring thumbnail images of the main actors from the movie or TV show's cast."
msgstr "Ka whakaatu i te rarangi i roto i nga tirohanga ataata e whakaatu ana i nga whakaahua karakōnui o nga kaiwhakaari matua mai i te kiriata, i te whakaaturanga pouaka whakaata ranei."

msgctxt "#31218"
msgid "Search the Studio Icons add-on for logo images of the film studios of the movie/TV show, and if found, display them while browsing the video views."
msgstr "Rapua te taapiri Ataata Ataata mo nga whakaahua moko o nga whare kiriata o te whakaaturanga kiriata/whakaata, a ki te kitea, whakaatu i a koe e tirotiro ana i nga tirohanga ataata."

msgctxt "#31219"
msgid "Search for the album's record label logo using the RecordLabel Icons addon, and if found, display it when browsing the music album views."
msgstr "Rapua te moko tapanga rekoata o te pukaemi ma te whakamahi i te taapiri RecordLabel Icons, a ki te kitea, whakaatu i te wa e tirotiro ana i nga tirohanga pukaemi puoro."

msgctxt "#31220"
msgid "Show rating"
msgstr "Whakaatu whakatauranga"

msgctxt "#31221"
msgid "Show artist clearart"
msgstr "Whakaatu toi toi clearart"

msgctxt "#31222"
msgid "Show CD"
msgstr "Whakaatu CD"

msgctxt "#31223"
msgid "Show Time"
msgstr "Whakaatu Wā"

msgctxt "#31224"
msgid "Animated posters"
msgstr "Nga panui pakiwaituhi"

msgctxt "#31225"
msgid "Normal posters"
msgstr "Panui panui noa"

msgctxt "#31226"
msgid "Extra posters"
msgstr "He panui taapiri"

msgctxt "#31227"
msgid "Sets the transparency level of the home menu widgets."
msgstr "Ka tautuhi i te taumata marama o nga widget tahua kaainga."

msgctxt "#31228"
msgid "Displays main menu options in a vertical layout instead of a horizontal one."
msgstr "Ka whakaatu i nga whiringa tahua matua i roto i te whakatakotoranga poutū, kaua ki te whakapae."

msgctxt "#31229"
msgid "Set another video file as startup intro"
msgstr "Tautuhia tetahi atu konae ataata hei intro whakaoho"

msgctxt "#31230"
msgid "Choose another video file to play when Kodi starts instead of Aeon Tajo default. It's recommended to choose a short one. To stop playback and start using Kodi right away, click or press any arrow key."
msgstr "Whiriwhiria tetahi atu konae ataata hei purei ina timata a Kodi hei utu mo Aeon Tajo taunoa.E taunaki ana kia whiriwhiria he mea poto.Hei whakamutu i te purei me te timata ki te whakamahi i a Kodi i tenei wa tonu, paohia, pehia ranei tetahi pere pere."

msgctxt "#31231"
msgid "Plays an intro video when launching Kodi"
msgstr "Ka purei i tetahi ataata whakataki i te wa e whakarewa ana a Kodi"

msgctxt "#31232"
msgid "Clear current intro video file and back to default"
msgstr "Ūkuia te kōnae ataata whakataki o nāianei ka hoki ki te taunoa"

msgctxt "#31233"
msgid "Clear the intro video file selected by the user and back to Aeon Tajo's default."
msgstr "Ūkuia te kōnae ataata whakataki i tohua e te kaiwhakamahi ka hoki ki te taunoa a Aeon Tajo."

msgctxt "#31234"
msgid "Adds a layer that simulates falling snow on all Kodi screens, with four available intensity levels."
msgstr "Ka taapirihia he paparanga e whakataurite ana i te hukarere i runga i nga mata katoa o Kodi, e wha nga taumata kaha e waatea ana."

msgctxt "#31235"
msgid "Override the current home menu backgrounds with this one"
msgstr "Whakakorehia nga papamuri tahua kaainga o naianei me tenei"

msgctxt "#31236"
msgid "The background selections made in the Setup Main Menu screen will be preserved. Disabling this option will restore all previous backgrounds. This option is particularly designed for use during special seasons."
msgstr "Ko nga kowhiringa papamuri i mahia i te mata Tahua Matua Tatūnga ka tiakina.Ko te whakakore i tenei kowhiringa ka whakahokia katoa nga papamuri o mua.Ko tenei waahanga kua tino hangaia mo te whakamahi i nga wa motuhake."

msgctxt "#31237"
msgid "No impact"
msgstr "Kaore he paanga"

msgctxt "#31238"
msgid "Very small"
msgstr "Tino iti"

msgctxt "#31239"
msgid "Small"
msgstr "Iti"

msgctxt "#31240"
msgid "Moderate"
msgstr "Whakaōrite"

msgctxt "#31241"
msgid "Pixel format"
msgstr "Hōputu pika"

msgctxt "#31242"
msgid "System rendering speed"
msgstr "Te tere tāhuahua pūnaha"

msgctxt "#31243"
msgid "Hide actor's thumbnails"
msgstr "Hunahia nga karakōnui o te kaiwhakaari"

msgctxt "#31244"
msgid "Show only a list of the actors' names, instead of also including their thumbnails."
msgstr "Whakaatuhia he rarangi ingoa anake o nga kaiwhakaari, kaua ki te whakauru i o raatau karakōnui."

msgctxt "#31250"
msgid "Automatic Full Screen when playing music"
msgstr "Mata Katoa Aunoa ina purei puoro"

msgctxt "#31251"
msgid "Don't play melodies while in Home Screen"
msgstr "Kaua e purei i nga waiata i a koe i te Mata Kainga"

msgctxt "#31252"
msgid "Always show home screen widgets"
msgstr "Whakaatu i nga wa katoa nga widget mata kaainga"

msgctxt "#31253"
msgid "Choose user audio playlist *.m3u (max.10 songs)"
msgstr "Kōwhirihia te rārangipāpāho ororongo kaiwhakamahi *.m3u (taunui 10 waiata)"

msgctxt "#31254"
msgid "Clear user playlist (back to default)"
msgstr "Ūkui rārangipāpāho kaiwhakamahi (hoki ki te taunoa)"

msgctxt "#31300"
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Tirohanga"

msgctxt "#31301"
msgid "Last Updated"
msgstr "Whakahoutanga Whakamutunga"

msgctxt "#31307"
msgid "Hide Fanart"
msgstr "Huna Fanart"

msgctxt "#31308"
msgid "Next aired"
msgstr "Whakapāho muri"

msgctxt "#31309"
msgid "Memory Used:"
msgstr "Mahara i Whakamahia:"

msgctxt "#31310"
msgid "Available audio tracks"
msgstr "Riri ororongo e waatea ana"

msgctxt "#31317"
msgid "Set Fanart Path"
msgstr "Whakaritea te Ara Fanart"

msgctxt "#31320"
msgid "Last Logged In"
msgstr "Takiuru Whakamutunga"

msgctxt "#31321"
msgid "Karaoke Song Selector"
msgstr "Kaiwhiri Waiata Karaoke"

msgctxt "#31328"
msgid "Recently Added"
msgstr "I tapirihia tata nei"

msgctxt "#31331"
msgid "Installed"
msgstr "Kua whakauruhia"

msgctxt "#31332"
msgid "Not Installed"
msgstr "Kāore i Tāutahia"

