msgid "Optional"
msgstr "Kōwhiringa"

msgctxt "#31390"
msgid "Skin default"
msgstr "Kiri taunoa"

msgctxt "#31400"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE INTERFACE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change the skin · Set language and region · Setup remote controls[CR]Set up a screensaver · Setup master lock"
msgstr "[B] WHAKATAUTANGA NGĀ TAUTAHI Atanga[/B][CR][CR]Hurihia te kiri · Tautuhi reo me te rohe · Tatūnga mana mamao[CR]Tauhia he tiaki mata · Tatūnga raka matua"

msgctxt "#31401"
msgid "Menu - press 'OK'"
msgstr "Tahua - pehia 'OK'"

msgctxt "#31402"
msgid "Enable startup video intro"
msgstr "Whakahohe intro ataata whakaoho"

msgctxt "#31405"
msgid "[B]MONITOR YOUR SYSTEM[/B][CR][CR]Check out your hardware · Monitor CPU usage[CR]Check Kodi revision number"
msgstr "[B] KAITIAKI I TO PUNA[/B][CR][CR]Tirohia to taputapu · Aroturuki te whakamahi PTM[CR]Tirohia te nama whakahou Kodi"

msgctxt "#31406"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SYSTEM SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup and calibrate displays · Configure audio output · [CR]Set power saving options · Enable debugging"
msgstr "[B] WHAKATAURANGA SYSTEM SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Tatūnga me te whakatika i nga whakaaturanga · Whirihorahia te whakaputa oro · [CR]Tautuhi i nga whiringa penapena hiko · Whakahohe te patuiro"

msgctxt "#31407"
msgid "[B]SETUP PROFILES[/B][CR][CR]Setup and manage user profiles · Enable login screen[CR]Change password · Add a profile picture"
msgstr "[B]KORERO WHAKATAHI[/B][CR][CR]Tautuhi me te whakahaere i nga kotaha kaiwhakamahi · Whakahohe te mata takiuru[CR]Huri kupuhipa · Tāpirihia he pikitia kōtaha"

msgctxt "#31409"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE TV SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change full screen info · Manage EPG data settings"
msgstr "[B] WHAKANUI NGA TAUTAHI TV[/B][CR][CR]Hurihia nga korero mata katoa · Whakahaerehia nga tautuhinga raraunga EPG"

msgctxt "#31410"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SERVICE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup control of Kodi via UPnP and HTTP · Configure file sharing[CR]Enable Zeroconf · Configure AirPlay"
msgstr "[B] WHAKANUI NGA TAUTAHI RATONGA[/B][CR][CR]Tatūnga mana o Kodi mā UPnP me HTTP · Whirihorahia te tiri kōnae[CR]Whakahohe Zeroconf · Whirihora AirPlay"

msgctxt "#31412"
msgid "Select section"
msgstr "Tīpakohia te waahanga"

msgctxt "#31413"
msgid "Local subtitle available"
msgstr "Taitararoto rohe e waatea ana"

msgctxt "#31414"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE PLAYER SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Configure video playback · Configure music playback · Configure picture slideshow[CR]Configure video language and subtitles"
msgstr "[B] WHAKATAURANGA TAUTAHI KAUPAPA KAUPAPA[/B][CR][CR]Whirihorahia te purei ataata · Whirihorahia te purei puoro · Whirihorahia te whakaatakiriata pikitia[CR] Whirihorahia te reo ataata me nga kupu hauraro"

msgctxt "#31415"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE MEDIA SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Set default select action · Configure file list options · Configure metadata options[CR]Manage databases"
msgstr "[B]WIRIHIA NGA TAUTAHI MEDIA[/B][CR][CR]Tautuhi i te mahi whiriwhiri taunoa · Whirihorahia nga whiringa rarangi konae · Whirihorahia nga whiringa metadata[CR]Whakahaerehia nga papaunga raraunga"

msgctxt "#31421"
msgid "Select your Kodi user profile[CR]to login and continue"
msgstr "Tīpakohia to kōtaha kaiwhakamahi Kodi [CR] ki te takiuru me te haere tonu"

msgctxt "#31427"
msgid "Skin Shortcuts is responsible for handling all aspects of the main menu."
msgstr "Ko nga Pokatata Kiri te kawenga mo te whakahaere i nga waahanga katoa o te tahua matua."

msgctxt "#31428"
msgid "The Grab Fanart script provides the random fanart slideshows for the main menu."
msgstr "Ko te tuhinga Grab Fanart e whakarato ana i nga whakaaturanga whakaataata matapōkere mo te tahua matua."

msgctxt "#31429"
msgid "Library Data Provider is a service that runs in the background to provide library data for widgets and live backgrounds as well as playlist statistics for infolines."
msgstr "Ko te Kaiwhakarato Raraunga Wharepukapuka he ratonga kei te papamuri ki te whakarato raraunga whare pukapuka mo nga widget me nga papamuri ora tae atu ki nga tatauranga raarangi mo nga raina korero."

msgctxt "#31430"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white studio icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "He taapiri whakaahua rauemi mo te whakaatu i nga tohu studio maamaa puta noa i te kiri."

msgctxt "#31431"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white recording label icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "He taapiri whakaahua rauemi mo te whakaatu i nga tohu tapanga rekoata ma puta noa i te kiri."

msgctxt "#31432"
msgid "Provides numerous Widget options and extended cast and crew metadata."
msgstr "He maha nga whiringa widget me nga metadata o nga kaitarai me nga kaimahi."

msgctxt "#31433"
msgid "Skin Info Service is used to display movie set information throughout the skin."
msgstr "Ka whakamahia te Ratonga Korero Kiri ki te whakaatu i nga korero huinga kiriata puta noa i te kiri."

msgctxt "#31434"
msgid "Check MP3 Theme checks whether the user has put a theme.mp3 file in the corresponding movie/TV show folder to be played when browsing."
msgstr "Tirohia te Kaupapa MP3 ka tirohia mena kua whakauruhia e te kaiwhakamahi tetahi konae kaupapa.mp3 ki te kōpaki kiriata/whakaata pouaka whakaata e tika ana hei purei ina tirotiro."

msgctxt "#31450"
msgid "  •  Open Settings "
msgstr "• Whakatuwherahia nga Tautuhinga"

msgctxt "#31451"
msgid "  •  Click to Install"
msgstr "• Pāwhiri ki te Tāuta"

msgctxt "#31473"
msgid "Aeon Tajo Helper provides the data to display the cast for movies and TV shows."
msgstr "Ko Aeon Tajo Helper e whakarato ana i nga raraunga hei whakaatu i nga kaitarai mo nga kiriata me nga whakaaturanga pouaka whakaata."

msgctxt "#31474"
msgid "CU LRC Lyrics is used to download, sync, and display lyrics during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Ka whakamahia nga Kupu CU LRC ki te tango, ki te tukutahi me te whakaatu i nga kupu i te wa o te purei puoro puoro."

msgctxt "#31475"
msgid "Play Trailer makes possible to play movie trailers through a context menu. "
msgstr "Ka taea e Play Trailer te purei i nga riipene kiriata ma te tahua horopaki."

msgctxt "#31476"
msgid "Allows the use of Youtube to play trailers and other videos."
msgstr "Whakaaetia te whakamahi i a Youtube ki te purei i nga waka me etahi atu ataata."

msgctxt "#31477"
msgid "Provides some cast actress images to be shown in video views."
msgstr "Ka whakaratohia etahi whakaahua kaitapere wahine hei whakaatu i nga tirohanga ataata."

msgctxt "#31478"
msgid "Artist Slideshow is used to display artist fanart for both the home screen and during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Ka whakamahia te Whakaaturanga Kiriata Toi hei whakaatu i te kaitoi kaitoi mo te mata o te kaainga me te purei puoro puoro."

msgctxt "#31479"
msgid "AutoCompletion provides suggestions to be selected while using the virtual keyboard."
msgstr "Ko te WhakaotiAunoa he whakaaro hei whiriwhiri ma te whakamahi i te papapātuhi mariko."

msgctxt "#31480"
msgid "Library Editor Script uses JSON to directly edit your database information."
msgstr "Ka whakamahi te Hōtuhi Kaiwhakatika Whare Pukapuka i a JSON ki te whakatika tika i o korero pātengi raraunga."

msgctxt "#31481"
msgid "Global Search makes possible to search among all the items (movies, TV shows, music, actors, etc.) in your collection."
msgstr "Ka taea e te Rapu Ao te rapu i roto i nga mea katoa (kiriata, whakaaturanga pouaka whakaata, waiata, kaiwhakaari, aha atu) i roto i to kohinga."

msgctxt "#31501"
msgid "Channel group"
msgstr "Rōpū hongere"

msgctxt "#31502"
msgid "Live TV"
msgstr "TV ora"

msgctxt "#31503"
msgid "Add Group"
msgstr "Tāpiri Rōpū"

msgctxt "#31504"
msgid "Rename Group"
msgstr "Whakaingoa ano te Rōpū"

msgctxt "#31505"
msgid "Delete Group"
msgstr "Muku Rōpū"

msgctxt "#31506"
msgid "Available[CR]Groups"
msgstr "Wātea [CR] Rōpū"

msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Channel Options"
msgstr "Kōwhiringa Hongere"

msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "Show similar movies in Shelf 3D view"
msgstr "Whakaatuhia nga kiriata rite ki te tirohanga Papa 3D"

msgctxt "#31901"
msgid "36 Hour Forecast"
msgstr "36 Haora Matapae"

msgctxt "#31902"
msgid "Hourly Forecast"
msgstr "Matapae-haora"

msgctxt "#31903"
msgid "Weekend Forecast"
msgstr "Matapae mo te wiki"

msgctxt "#31904"
msgid "10 Day Forecast"
msgstr "10 Ra Matapae"

msgctxt "#31908"
msgid "Chance of Precipitation"
msgstr "Tuponotanga o te ua"

msgctxt "#31909"
msgid "Fetching forecast info..."
msgstr "Tiki korero matapae..."

msgctxt "#31910"
msgid "Map & Alerts"
msgstr "Mapi & Matohi"

msgctxt "#31911"
msgid "Setup the Aeon Tajo main menu"
msgstr "Whakaritea te tahua matua Aeon Tajo"

msgctxt "#31912"
msgid "Customize the main menu with widgets, backgrounds and statistics. Add your own custom main menu items."
msgstr "Whakaritehia te tahua matua me nga widget, papamuri me nga tatauranga.Tāpirihia ō ake tūemi tahua matua ritenga."

msgctxt "#31913"
msgid "Aeon Tajo main menu vertical position"
msgstr "Aeon Tajo tahua matua tūnga poutū"

msgctxt "#31914"
msgid "Change the vertical position of the main menu. Default is centered on screen."
msgstr "Hurihia te tūnga poutū o te tahua matua.Ko te taunoa kei waenganui i te mata."

msgctxt "#31915"
msgid "Navigation style for horizontal lists"
msgstr "Kāhua whakaterenga mō ngā rārangi whakapae"

msgctxt "#31916"
msgid "Change the way horizontal lists scroll in Aeon Tajo. Default will scroll lists in a cycle. \"Fixed\" are lists with a beginning and end."
msgstr "Hurihia te huarahi panuku rarangi whakapae i Aeon Tajo.Ko te taunoa ka panuku nga rarangi i roto i te huringa.Ko te \"Whakatika\" he rarangi timatanga me te mutunga."

msgctxt "#31917"
msgid "When enabled text scrolls automatically. When disabled manual scrolling is required. Note that most textboxes don't have a manual button."
msgstr "Ina whakahohea ka panuku aunoa.I te wa e hiahiatia ana te panuku a-ringa.Kia mahara ko te nuinga o nga pouaka kuputuhi kaore he paatene a-ringa."

msgctxt "#31918"
msgid "Projects the current playing video on the background behind the panels."
msgstr "Ka whakatakotohia te riipene whakaata o naianei ki te papamuri i muri o nga panui."

msgctxt "#31919"
msgid "Projects the visualisation on the background behind the panels when music is played."
msgstr "Ka whakatakotohia te tirohanga ki te papamuri i muri o nga panui ka whakatangihia te puoro."

msgctxt "#31920"
msgid "Displays a widget on the Home screen with media information when music is playing."
msgstr "Ka whakaatu i tetahi widget ki te mata o te Kainga me nga korero pāpāho i te wa e purei ana te puoro."

msgctxt "#31921"
msgid "Displays a widget on the Home screen with media information when a movie or episode is playing."
msgstr "Ka whakaatu i tetahi widget ki te mata o te Kainga me nga korero pāpāho i te wa e purei ana tetahi kiriata, wahanga ranei."

msgctxt "#31922"
msgid "This enables custom genre backgrounds when browsing through the videolibrary's genre node. Filenames should match the genre label. Extension must be .jpg."
msgstr "Ma tenei ka taea nga papamuri momo ritenga i te wa e tirotiro ana i roto i te node momo o te whare pukapuka ataata.Me taurite nga ingoa kōnae ki te tapanga momo.Ko te toronga me .jpg."

msgctxt "#31923"
msgid "Set a default select action to enable this item."
msgstr "Tautuhia he hohenga whiriwhiri taunoa kia taea ai tenei mea."

msgctxt "#31924"
msgid "This enables custom genre backgrounds when browsing through the musiclibrary's genre node. Filenames should match the genre label. Extension must be .jpg."
msgstr "Ma tenei ka taea nga papamuri momo ritenga i te wa e tirotiro ana i roto i te node momo o te whare pukapuka puoro.Me taurite nga ingoa kōnae ki te tapanga momo.Ko te toronga me .jpg."

msgctxt "#31925"
msgid "Pick one of the preset backgrounds or set your own images as the menu items background."
msgstr "Whiriwhiria tetahi o nga papamuri tatūkē, tautuhia ranei o ake whakaahua hei papamuri o nga taonga tahua."

msgctxt "#31926"
msgid "Select add-ons, playlists or favourites. Choose 'Custom' for any of Kodi's built-in functions. (http://kodi.wiki/?title=List_of_Built_In_Functions)"
msgstr "Tīpakohia ngā tāpiri-ake, rārangipāpāho me ngā makau.Kōwhirihia te 'Ritenga' mo tetahi o nga mahi hanga-i roto a Kodi.(http://kodi.wiki/?title=List_of_Built_In_Functions)"

msgctxt "#31927"
msgid "Resets all above values to their defaults."
msgstr "Ka tautuhi ano i nga uara o runga ake ki o raatau taunoa."

msgctxt "#31928"
msgid "Aeon Tajo main menu layout"
msgstr "Aeon Tajo tahora tahua matua"

msgctxt "#31929"
msgid "This setting defines how much items will be visible on the main menu. Options are 3 items or 5 items."
msgstr "Ka tautuhia e tenei tautuhinga te nui o nga mea ka kitea ki te tahua matua.Ko nga whiringa he 3 tuemi, 5 ranei nga taonga."

msgctxt "#31930"
msgid "Choose a widget to display on the Home screen to have easy access to content from the library."
msgstr "Kōwhirihia he widget hei whakaatu ki te mata o te Kāinga kia ngawari te uru ki nga ihirangi mai i te whare pukapuka."

msgctxt "#31931"
msgid "Video plot preference"
msgstr "Te manakohanga papahanga ataata"

msgctxt "#31932"
msgid "Show plot outline in the library views and full plot in the video information dialog or vice versa. Falls back to full plot if no outline is available."
msgstr "Whakaatuhia te whakahuahua mahere i roto i nga tirohanga whare pukapuka me te katoa o nga mahere i roto i te korero korero ataata, he rereke ranei.Ka hoki ki te papa katoa mena karekau he whakahuahua e waatea ana."

msgctxt "#31933"
msgid "Select an item to display on the left top of the main menu"
msgstr "Tīpakohia he tūemi hei whakaatu ki te taha mauī o runga o te tahua matua"

msgctxt "#31935"
msgid "Switch places with another menu item. Opens a dialog with a list of menu items to choose from."
msgstr "Hurihia nga waahi me tetahi atu mea tahua.Ka whakatuwherahia he korero me te rarangi o nga mea tahua hei whiriwhiri."

msgctxt "#31937"
msgid "Show the RSS feed on the bottom or top of the screen, depending on main menu position. Enabling this setting makes the submenu permanently visible."
msgstr "Whakaatuhia te whāngai RSS ki raro, ki runga ranei o te mata, i runga i te turanga tahua matua.Ma te whakahohe i tenei tautuhinga ka kitea tonutia te tahuaroto."

msgctxt "#31938"
msgid "Enables extra information in the TV show library, like TV show status, next / latest episode, etc. Depends on TV Show Next Aired add-on."
msgstr "Whakahohe ai i etahi atu korero i roto i te whare pukapuka whakaaturanga pouaka whakaata, penei i te mana o te whakaaturanga pouaka whakaata, te wahanga o muri/hou, me era atu. Kei runga ake i te Whakaaturanga TV Whakaputanga Paanui Panuku."

msgctxt "#31939"
msgid "Hide Infopanel on scrolling"
msgstr "Hunahia te Panui korero i te panuku"

msgctxt "#31940"
msgid "Hides the infopanel for Showcase and Landscape view (if activated) while scrolling through the library. Set the amount of seconds to wait for the infopanel to appear when scrolling is stopped."
