msgctxt "#31290"
msgid "Thanks for using Aeon Tajo—I really hope you’re enjoying it. Creating and maintaining a Kodi skin like this takes hundreds of hours of work. If Aeon Tajo is something you enjoy and find useful, supporting it helps me keep working on it and ensures it can continue evolving in the future. [CR][CR]If you decide to do so, you’ll receive frequent updates with new features and bug fixes, along with videos, media packs, and easy-to-follow articles with detailed tips to help you get the most out of everything Aeon Tajo has to offer, together with my sincere gratitude for your support. [CR][CR]For more information, visit [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] and search for the creator [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], or go to [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Thanks!"
msgstr "Nga mihi mo te whakamahi i a Aeon Tajo—Kei te tino tumanako ahau kei te pai koe.Ko te hanga me te pupuri i te kiri Kodi penei he maha nga haora o te mahi.Mena he mea pai a Aeon Tajo ki a koe, ka kitea e koe he mea whai hua, ko te tautoko i tera ka awhina i ahau ki te mahi tonu me te whakarite kia tipu tonu a meake nei.[CR][CR]Ki te whakatau koe ki te pera, ka whiwhi koe i nga whakahōutanga maha me nga ahuatanga hou me nga whakatika pepeha, me nga riipene whakaata, nga paapaki pāpāho, me nga tuhinga ngawari ki te whai me nga tohutohu taipitopito hei awhina i a koe ki te whai hua i nga mea katoa ka tukuna e Aeon Tajo, me taku mihi aroha mo to tautoko.[CR][CR]Mo etahi atu korero, haere ki [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] ka rapu mo te kaihanga [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], haere ranei ki [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR]!"

